{"tid":320184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"坐小巴同阿婆既對話","createTime":"2017-07-13T10:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T18:26:11.000Z","uid":79410,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a0d885ca40493dfa39fabf55a67fcc2798e9bd7","tid":320184,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:56:11.000Z","msg":"阿婆自言自語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />後生幾多歲丫, 俾佢30歲, 咪最多做左十幾年人, 冇大陸香港有水飲?冇大陸香港有菜食?<br />\n我: 阿婆.你就好啦, 飲水食菜都唔使錢.<br />\n阿婆: 咩唔洗錢呀? 俾錢買架! <br />\n我: 咁我地都要多謝日本啦. D 人成日反日反日, 做左幾多年人丫.<br />\n阿婆: D 籮白頭打我地香港,個時幾咁淒涼呀! 做乜要多謝佢地.<br />\n我: 個時淒涼, 你而家咪幸福囉, 唔係籮白頭賣俾我地香港, 我地邊有小巴坐咁舒服呀?!<br />\n阿婆: 有冇搞錯, 你死仔包黎架你, 你冇用架.......................<br />\n<br />\n點解D 阿婆講黎講去都係講個幾句? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767aff160a0b4d484802123cd1e9d95d312422ed","tid":320184,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:59:03.000Z","msg":"激到阿婆爆血管你就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fee3a90d8ae358a6a10fdf01e43df178a97f41","tid":320184,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:03:38.000Z","msg":"串鳩埋阿婆<br />\n<br />\n你係咪用火煲飯食？<br />\n<br />\n冇日本你仲要用火煲飯呀，邊有電飯煲煲飯你食。"},{"pid":"11f144126e1e62a12ba2f68c310f3888fecdc6b6","tid":320184,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>串鳩埋阿婆<br />\n<br />\n你係咪用火煲飯食？<br />\n<br />\n冇日本你仲要用火煲飯呀，邊有電飯煲煲飯你食。</blockquote><br />\n個阿婆嘈左好鬼耐, 臨到總站先串佢.<br />\n串完拍拍籮油走人.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc426ff6ae979a96160946ea1c56be09bc3984a","tid":320184,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:53:20.000Z","msg":"沒有共產黨 哪有新中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沒有日本仔 哪有新香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34262d785feb99400ca2c8edd166df71a7b706af","tid":320184,"uid":31219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:06:22.000Z","msg":"如果阿婆爆血管死左，樓主會唔會比人charge誤殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1536cbf6477bb9b3677af03edfb5fc3113f4e6fb","tid":320184,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:08:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果阿婆爆血管死左，樓主會唔會比人charge誤殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兇器係念力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600e747539ba6342c91c0fa58c6fbfc36c3500f7","tid":320184,"uid":130495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ad82ac4423e93a09ae6ca8035f693b0b1dddb4","tid":320184,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:26:11.000Z","msg":"到死嗰日都仲活喺虛幻嘅世界入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}